com.blockwithme.util.xtend

Class ScalarExtension

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.blockwithme.util.shared.Preconditions
      • com.blockwithme.util.xtend.JavaUtilLoggingExtension
        • com.blockwithme.util.xtend.ScalarExtension
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BooleanExtension

    public class ScalarExtension
extends JavaUtilLoggingExtension
    Xtend Extension related to "scalar" values. The goal is to allow to easily get the "scale/size/length" of a value.
    Author:
    monster
